into a car of three Mexican nationals suspected of killing a
Phoenix policeman. The police union gives him a $500 reward and a
certificate for a replacement gun. Another man opens fire, along
with police, on a suspect in the shooting death of a girl in a
north Phoenix apartment complex on Peoria Avenue three months ago.
Police never even released his name. By MARK SHAFFER. Story will
