   OBIT-WILLIAMS (Undated) _ Joe Williams, whose urbane
bass-baritone and suavely heartbroken songs made him one of the
most important singers in jazz, died in Las Vegas, Nev. He was 80
years old. By Jon Pareles. (Scheduled to move by 8:30 p.m. ET in
