<P>
   BOTTLED-WATER (Washington) _ People who buy bottled water cannot
be sure that it is purer or safer than tap water, an environmental
advocacy group said after sampling 1,000 bottles of water sold
under 103 brand names. By John H. Cushman Jr.
</P>
<P>
   AIRLINES-DISABLED (Washington) _ Disabled air travelers are
frequently mistreated by airline personnel and denied special
accommodations including access to wheelchairs and escorts in
violation of a 1986 law, according to the National Council on
Disability.
</P>
