<P>
   BKN-JORDAN (Undated) _ Suddenly, there are rumors that Michael
Jordan will come out of retirement to play for the Charlotte
Hornets, possibly as part of a deal in which he would purchase a 50
percent interest in the team. The scenario _ right out of Hollywood
_ even has Phil Jackson as the new coach and Dean Smith, Jordan's
college coach at North Carolina, as the team president. By Mike
Wise.
