<P>
   HKN-ISLES-PANTHERS (Miami) _ Islanders at Florida, 7:30 p.m. ET
start. By Tarik El-Bashir.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-DEVILS-DUCKS (East Rutherford, N.J.) _ Anaheim at Devils,
7:30 p.m. ET start. By Alex Yannis.
</P>
