   BKC-UGA-HARRICK _ Profile on the 60-year-old Jim Harrick, who
has spent more than 25 years in college coaching. Harrick has
enjoyed the ultimate success, leading UCLA to the national title in
1995, but has also spent time at the bottom, spending one year away
from coaching after his firing from UCLA for falsifying an expense
report. (Wilkinson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
