A1261 &Cx1f; tad-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NATO-SECURITY01-COX     03-31 0631
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NATO-SECURITY01-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SECURITY WILL BE TIGHT FOR NATO SUMMIT IN U.S.
 &HT;    By BOB DART
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
