<HEADLINE>
MOVIES: ``FORCES OF NATURE'' 
 FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE 
 FROM THE FORT WORTH STAR-TELEGRAM
</HEADLINE>
  World rights. 
 Includes one color slide of actors Ben Affleck and Sandra Bullock
in a scene from the movie ``Forces of Nature.'' (Credit: Photo by
Darren Michaels. Copyright 1998 Dreamworks.) 
 By BECKY REGAN, High School Student 
 Copyright 1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``FORCES OF NATURE''
</P>
<P>
   Starring: Sandra Bullock, Ben Affleck.
</P>
<P>
   Plot: Ben is trying to get to his wedding. The only problem is
everything is going wrong. He meets Sara, who is a
spur-of-the-moment kind of person. When these opposites meet,
disaster strikes.
</P>
<P>
   Why Go See It?: It is a great movie, full of surprises and
laughs. Never a dull moment.
</P>
<P>
