   NY-DIALLO-INDICT (New York) _ Four New York City police officers
are arraigned on charges of second-degree murder and suspended from
the police force in the shooting death of Amadou Diallo, marking a
new stage in a case that has riveted, and riven, the city for
weeks. By Amy Waldman. (Scheduled to move by 8:30 p.m. ET in ``a''
news file.)
</P>
