by a man attending a demonstration in support of the police outside
the courthouse. Carroll and three other New York City police
officers were arraigned on charges of second-degree murder and
suspended from the police force Wednesday in the shooting death of
Amadou Diallo. (Librado Romero/New York Times Photo)
